    "reviews": [
      "A vain Queen visits her mirror each day to have it confirmed that she is the fairest in the land. When, one morning, her validator gives her news less to her liking she determines to have her step daughter \"Snow White\" done away with. Her c"
    ],
    "backdrop_url": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/duguBoss/daily-movie-hub@main/data/images/movie_408_b.jpg",
    "poster_url": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/duguBoss/daily-movie-hub@main/data/images/movie_408_p.jpg",
